---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { PRICING, formatPrice } from '~/utils/pricing';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Next Steps | SellOnTube',
  description: 'You are interested. Here is exactly what getting started with SellOnTube looks like.',
  robots: 'noindex, nofollow',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mb-3">You are in</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Here is exactly what getting started looks like
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Five steps from here to your first video live on YouTube.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Steps -->
  <section class="pb-16 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-10">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Choose the plan that fits where you are right now</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Foundation ({formatPrice(PRICING.foundation)}/mo) is strategy-led: your team handles execution with our direction. Growth ({formatPrice(PRICING.growth)}/mo) is where we take on scripting and lead capture too. Scale ({formatPrice(PRICING.scale)}/mo) is fully hands-off for you.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Most B2B SaaS teams start at Growth. You can always move up after month 4 once you see what is working.
          </p>
          <a href="/pricing" class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 hover:underline">
            See full plan comparison &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"></div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">We sort the paperwork quickly</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Once you confirm the plan, we send a simple service agreement the same day. The minimum engagement is 4 months. That is the honest minimum to see compounding results from YouTube. After month 4, you are free to continue, pause, or walk away. No pressure either way.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Payment is monthly, billed at the start of each month.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"></div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">We do a proper knowledge transfer before a single script is written</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            This is not a single onboarding call. We take roughly three weeks to genuinely understand your business. That means walkthroughs with your sales team, access to your product, going through your existing documentation and marketing materials, and calls with you directly on brand voice, positioning, and vision.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            We will also need read-only access to Google Search Console and Google Analytics, and Manager access on YouTube Studio so we can handle SEO and publishing directly. We walk you through all of that.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            At the end of this phase you get a documented brief: a written summary of how we understand your product, your buyer, and your positioning. You read it, confirm it is accurate, and then we start scripting. Nothing moves forward until you say that brief is right.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"></div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">4</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">We build your content roadmap</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Month 1 is strategy. We research keywords, map competitor content, and put together a 90-day topic roadmap built entirely around buyer intent. Every topic has verified search demand. You review and approve before we start scripting.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Your involvement this month: the onboarding call and one async review. That is genuinely it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"></div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="flex gap-5">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">5</div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Your first video goes live</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Typically in week 4 from the day you sign, once the knowledge transfer phase is complete and the brief is approved. We handle scripting, voiceover, editing, thumbnails, SEO, and publishing. You review async and answer the occasional question.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
            Most clients are spending 5 to 6 hours a month once the system is up and running.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What you bring -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">What we need from you</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
          Confirmed plan choice and signed agreement
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
          YouTube Studio Manager access (we will send you the exact steps)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
          60 minutes for the onboarding call
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
          Async reviews on topic roadmap and scripts (we give you clear prompts, not blank pages)
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-bold mt-0.5">✓</span>
          A point of contact on your side for ongoing alignment
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Ready to move forward?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-300">
        Let Gautham know which plan you want to start with and he will take it from there.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/919400474785"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold bg-black text-white hover:bg-gray-900 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
          WhatsApp Gautham
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:gautham@sellontube.com"
          class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Email Gautham
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-500">
        Or book a quick call if you prefer:
        <a href="https://cal.com/gautham-8bdvdx/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-slate-300">cal.com/gautham</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
